The '''Fromm Gang'''<ref name="War of the Bounty Hunters 2">[[War of the Bounty Hunters 2|''War of the Bounty Hunters'' 2]]</ref> was an organization. [[Han Solo]] and [[Chewbacca]] once performed a [[Fromm job|job]] that related to the Fromm Gang and, in the process, hired someone to help them, with Solo later wondering if the individual in question was the [[Gamorrean]] [[pirate]] [[Na'Vrokk]].<ref name="Smuggler's Guide">''[[Star Wars: Smuggler's Guide]]''</ref>

